premise_source_doc_sentence: Transgender people are sometimes called transsexual if they desire medical assistance to transition from one sex to another .

claim: Transgender people are called transsexual if they have medical procedures that alter their anatomy.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Sex reassignment surgery or SRS  (  also known as gender reassignment surgery , genital reconstruction surgery , gender confirmation surgery or sex realignment surgery  )  is the surgical procedure  (  or procedures  )  by which a transgender person 's physical appearance and function of their existing sexual characteristics are altered to resemble that socially associated with their identified gender .
